&lt;h1&gt;Senior Talent Partner&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6–9 month fixed-term opportunity.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; We&#39;re also happy to hear from exceptional fractional Talent Partners whose availability aligns with our hiring plans. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;While this role is initially designed as a fixed-term engagement, we&#39;re always excited to invest in exceptional talent as our business continues to grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About Plooto&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Plooto is a Canada-born fintech company on a mission to give small and mid-sized businesses the financial power to succeed on their own terms.&amp;nbsp; We make payments secure, accurate, and stress-free so businesses and their accountants can spend less time in the books, confidently manage cash flow, and make smarter decisions every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We&#39;re building a company where talented people can do the best work of their careers.&amp;nbsp; We believe the way you hire determines the company you become, and we&#39;re looking for someone who believes that too.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;You probably aren&#39;t looking for just another recruiter role.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You&#39;re looking for a company that believes hiring is a competitive advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You believe every hire shapes culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You think candidate experience is a product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You care as much about coaching hiring managers to make better decisions as you do about finding exceptional people.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You&#39;ve already started experimenting with AI because you know hiring is changing, and you&#39;re excited to help define what comes next.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;If this sounds like you, keep reading.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a builder.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;As our Senior Talent Partner, you&#39;ll partner directly with our Chief People Officer and leaders across the business to help build the next chapter of Talent at Plooto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll help leaders make exceptional hiring decisions, uncover remarkable talent, design thoughtful interview experiences, and build an AI-native recruiting function that allows people to spend less time on administrative work and more time exercising judgment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Some days you&#39;ll be discussing organizational design and hiring strategy with senior leaders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Some days you&#39;ll be developing sourcing strategies and messaging, reviewing interview feedback, or closing an exceptional candidate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We don&#39;t think those are different jobs.&amp;nbsp; We think that&#39;s what great Talent Partners do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead full-cycle hiring across technical and business functions, partnering with hiring managers from role definition through offer acceptance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop thoughtful sourcing strategies that consistently uncover exceptional talent, not simply active applicants.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach hiring managers to become stronger interviewers and better hiring decision-makers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and continuously improve structured interview experiences that raise hiring quality while delivering an exceptional candidate experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define what an AI-native recruiting function looks
